            <thetext>The problem with Opera is that it does not fire a &quot;beforeunload&quot; event: 
http://my.opera.com/community/forums/topic.dml?id=205955
We use this event to prompt the user to continue unloading or to cancel it. 
Opera does not support canceling closing windows/tabs, anyway...

Perhaps you can overwrite terminate() to do some last things before the 
application gets destroyed.</thetext>
          </long_desc>
